flowchart TB
  Title["Distributed Rate Limiter<br/>Request Path + State Model"]:::title
  Legend["Solid = request path<br/>State nodes show single-node and distributed enforcement"]:::legend
  Title ~~~ Legend

  subgraph RequestPath["Request Path"]
    direction LR
    Client(["API client"]):::actor --> Api["Go HTTP API<br/>POST /check"]:::app --> Gate["RateLimiter interface"]:::app --> Impl["Limiter implementation<br/>fixed / sliding / token bucket"]:::worker --> Api
  end

  subgraph State["Enforcement State"]
    direction LR
    Local[("Mutex window state<br/>FixedWindowLimiter")]:::db
    Lua["Lua engines<br/>INCR / TIME / TTL"]:::worker
    Redis[("Redis keys / hashes<br/>window buckets + token state")]:::db
    Note["Fail-closed on Redis errors<br/>Tests use miniredis + injected time"]:::legend
  end

  Legend ~~~ Client
  Impl -->|single-node mode| Local
  Impl -->|distributed modes| Lua -->|atomic update| Redis
  Redis -->|allow / deny| Impl
  Note ~~~ Redis

